From: Matthias Clasen <mclasen@redhat.com>
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 2025 10:07:32 -0500
Subject: build: Reshuffle docs build

Make this match closer what gtk does, and make the documentation
and man-pages options independent of each other, so man pages
can build without documentation.

Fixes: #840
(cherry picked from commit ff21759b7634505f8b1a529f7950e6617a59d80f)
---
 docs/meson.build | 283 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---------------------------
 meson.build      |   9 +-
 2 files changed, 150 insertions(+), 142 deletions(-)

